{"title":"听叮咚","authors":["王树元"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"听叮咚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔听黎族老人王玉梅演奏黎族打击乐曲《打叮咚》有感〕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王树元"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是在民族宫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是在椰林中？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是木梆声声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是心弦铮铮？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白发飘飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木键儿弹出了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"串串心声——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"键儿轻："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五指山腰落秋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨打椰树叶飘零。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汪汪的苦水呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黎族老人的心头涌……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"键儿重："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南海波涛怒腾腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雷雨电天摇动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一杆子红旗哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引千万黎胞闹革命！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"键儿紧："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀挑破山中雾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号角吹落满天星。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京的太阳呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得琼崖宝岛天大明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"键儿松："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朵朵红云送春风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山山水水笑盈盈。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"甜甜的清泉哪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洗得黎山瑶岭绿溶溶……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叮叮、咚咚咚咚、叮叮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你弹出："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点泪水声声笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你弹出："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万黎胞心中情。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"键儿住了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么大厅里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还响着叮咚、叮咚？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊！原来是，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人眼望中南海呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心中唱起“东方红……”"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}